# flan-t5-tacred-kg-w-context-small

[flan-t5-small](https://huggingface.co/google/flan-t5-small) trained over the TACRED Knowledge Graph using the training method for [KGT-5](https://github.com/apoorvumang/kgt5/) with additional sentences alongside the prompts.
